Quick Search for Folders
Use to find folders within the Lightning Reports tab, Dashboards tab, or selected folder context.
Available in: Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

Find the quick search box at the top of each report, dashboard, and folder page. Select a scope on the side menu and start entering text to see the list of matches within the selected scope.

Quick search shows only the first 20 results. A message indicates if there are more results that arenâ€™t showing.
The context is always what is selected on the side menu.
Quick search finds all folders and subfolders, but not reports and dashboards in the folders.
The options to customize columns and create folders are disabled during quick search.
Quick search keeps the current custom column selections and sorting.
title: Using Quick Search in Salesforce Analytics
